---
title: BBQ Sriracha Pork & Rainbow Veggie Fries with Cheddar Cheese & Slaw
description: Cheesy, saucy and smokey — this American-style concoction is an explosion of colour and flavour! From the tasty
BBQ pork to the rainbow fries and creamy slaw for crunch, every bite will knock your socks off!

